---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About ProxyFAQs | The Stack Overflow for Proxies"
  description="Learn about ProxyFAQs, the vendor-neutral knowledge platform for proxy and web scraping questions."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-50 via-white to-white py-16">
    <div class="container-custom text-center">
      <p class="badge-primary mx-auto w-fit mb-4">About</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-secondary-900 mb-4">About ProxyFAQs</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-secondary-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        The Stack Overflow for proxies — a vendor-neutral knowledge platform built for real-world
        data collection.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom space-y-10">
      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-900 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-secondary-600 mb-4">
          ProxyFAQs is built to solve a simple problem: finding reliable, vendor-neutral information
          about proxies is hard.
        </p>
        <p class="text-secondary-600 mb-4">
          Today, developers and businesses waste hours searching through:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-secondary-600 space-y-2">
          <li>Outdated blog posts from 2018</li>
          <li>Reddit threads with conflicting advice</li>
          <li>Vendor marketing materials disguised as guides</li>
          <li>Scattered forum discussions across dozens of sites</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-secondary-600 mt-4">
          We're building the definitive knowledge hub where you can find answers to 1M+ questions,
          compare providers with real data, and get instant help from an AI trained on 10 years of
          proxy expertise.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-900 mb-6">What Makes Us Different</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-secondary-50">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-2">Vendor Neutral</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary-600">
              We're not owned by any proxy provider. Our recommendations are based on real data and
              community feedback, not who pays us the most.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-secondary-50">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-2">Data-Driven</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary-600">
              Every answer is backed by real-world data. We've analyzed 1M+ questions people
              actually ask Google about proxies and web scraping.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-secondary-50">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-2">AI-Powered</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary-600">
              Our AI chat assistant is trained on 10 years of proxy expertise. It understands your
              specific use case and provides contextual recommendations.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-secondary-50">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-2">Always Up-to-Date</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary-600">
              Proxy providers change their offerings constantly. We track pricing, features, and
              performance so you don't have to.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-900 mb-6">Who We Serve</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-secondary-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-2">Developers</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary-600">
              Software engineers building scrapers, bots, and data pipelines who need technical
              answers fast.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-secondary-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-2">Businesses</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary-600">
              E-commerce sellers, SEO agencies, and data companies who need reliable proxy
              solutions.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-secondary-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-2">Learners</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary-600">
              Students and hobbyists who want to understand proxies without getting lost in jargon.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-900 mb-4">Transparency</h2>
        <p class="text-secondary-600 mb-4">
          We believe in full transparency about how we make money:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-secondary-600 space-y-2">
          <li>Some provider links are affiliate links — we earn a commission if you sign up</li>
          <li>Affiliate status never affects our rankings or recommendations</li>
          <li>All affiliate links are clearly marked with a disclosure</li>
          <li>We only recommend providers we've personally tested or verified</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-900 mb-4">Built in Public</h2>
        <p class="text-secondary-600 mb-4">ProxyFAQs is built using modern web technologies:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-secondary-600 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>Astro 4.x for lightning-fast static generation</li>
          <li>Supabase PostgreSQL for our knowledge base</li>
          <li>VectorEngine API (grok-4-fast) for AI chat</li>
          <li>Cloudflare Pages for global edge delivery</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-secondary-600">
          We're committed to building the best proxy knowledge platform in the world.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-900 mb-4">Get in Touch</h2>
        <p class="text-secondary-600 mb-6">
          Have questions, suggestions, or want to partner with us?
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/search" class="btn-primary"> Browse Questions </a>
          <a href="/providers" class="btn-secondary"> Compare Providers </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
